List of simulation tests
========================

McVine simulations
------------------

Config file        | Simulation chain
-------------------+-----------------

ssd1.pml            [Source_simple] -> [V_sample] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]
ssd1_1.pml          [Source_simple] -> [V_sample] -> [TOF_monitor]
ssd1_2.pml          [Source_simple] -> [V_sample] -> [E_monitor]
ssd2.pml            [Source_simple] -> [PowderKernel] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]  for Al.laz
ssd2_1.pml          [Source_simple] -> [PowderKernel] -> [TOF_monitor]      for Al_2.laz
ssd2_2.pml          [Source_simple] -> [PowderKernel] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]  for Al_2.laz
ssd2_3.pml          [Source_simple] -> [PowderN] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]       for Al_2.laz
ssd3.pml            [SNS_source4] -> [PowderKernel] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]    for Al.laz
ssd4.pml            [SNS_source4] -> [PowderKernel] -> [DetectorSystem]     for Al.laz
ssd4_1.pml          [Source_simple] -> [PowderKernel] -> [DetectorSystem]   for Al.laz
ssd5.pml            [Source_simple] -> [PowderKernel] -> [NDMonitor]        for Al.laz
ssd5_1.pml          [Source_simple] -> [PowderN] -> [NDMonitor]

McStas simulations
------------------
ssd2.inst           [Source_simple] -> [PowderN] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]       for Al.laz
ssd2_2.inst         [Source_simple] -> [PowderN] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]       for Al_2.laz
ssd2_3.inst         [Source_simple] -> [PowderN] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI] (different parameters)
ssd3.inst           [SNS_source4] -> [PowderN] -> [PSD_monitor_4PI]

Results
--------

Results are located in directory "results/" in corresponding directory. E.g. example ssd5.pml
has results in "results/ssd5" directory
